name: C64 Birthday logo jam in LOGO
name_original: C64 Birthday logo jam in LOGO
description:
The Commodore logo in LOGO to celebrate the C64's birthday.

This demo's seed code comes from the classic SYDFLOWER demo found on the examples disk, then heavily modified. The procedure and superprocedure names are unmodified as homage to the original DAISY author Syd Lexia.
